caption: Last week was a moment that I will forever cherish… to receive the IMPACT AWARD from the phenomenal @HumanRightsCampaign, presented with such heartfelt words from THE @shrrycola (everything you said, is exactly how we all feel about you Sherry), amongst an immeasurable amount of love and support was a truly humbling honor. Over the years, I’ve realized firsthand that allyship is more than a label; it’s an action. Thank you to the HRC for the powerful and imperative work that you do to protect the human rights that every person deserves ❤️
